29-30 May - Cream Filling

1 cup milk, scalded
3 tablespoons flour
1/4 cup sugar
1/4 teaspoon salt
2 egg yolks or 1 egg
1/2 teaspoon vanilla

Mix sugar, flour, salt in a bowl, stir in scalded milk. Return mixture to double boiler. Stir over boiling water until mixture has thickened. Cover ??? ??? while beating the egg yolks, stir a little of the hot milk mixture into the yolks, stir the diluted yolks into the cantents of the dobule boiler. Cook 1 minute. Remove from stove, add vanilla and cool. 